quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  92,15,"la ydkhlha 'iilaa man kan shadid alshqa', aladhi kdhdhab nabiin allah mhmdana salaa allah ealayh wslm, wa'aerid ean al'iiman biallah wrswlh, wtaethma"
  92,16,"la ydkhlha 'iilaa man kan shadid alshqa', aladhi kdhdhab nabiin allah mhmdana salaa allah ealayh wslm, wa'aerid ean al'iiman biallah wrswlh, wtaethma"
  92,17,"wsyuzhzah eanha shadid altqwa, aldhy ybdhl malah abtigha' almazid min alkhyr. walays 'iinfaquh dhak mkafat liman asda 'iilayh merwfa, lknh ybtghy bdhlk wajh rabih al'aelaa wrdah, walasawf yetyh allah fi aljanat ma yardaa bh"
  92,18,"wsyuzhzah eanha shadid altqwa, aldhy ybdhl malah abtigha' almazid min alkhyr. walays 'iinfaquh dhak mkafat liman asda 'iilayh merwfa, lknh ybtghy bdhlk wajh rabih al'aelaa wrdah, walasawf yetyh allah fi aljanat ma yardaa bh"
  92,19,"wsyuzhzah eanha shadid altqwa, aldhy ybdhl malah abtigha' almazid min alkhyr. walays 'iinfaquh dhak mkafat liman asda 'iilayh merwfa, lknh ybtghy bdhlk wajh rabih al'aelaa wrdah, walasawf yetyh allah fi aljanat ma yardaa bh"
  92,20,"wsyuzhzah eanha shadid altqwa, aldhy ybdhl malah abtigha' almazid min alkhyr. walays 'iinfaquh dhak mkafat liman asda 'iilayh merwfa, lknh ybtghy bdhlk wajh rabih al'aelaa wrdah, walasawf yetyh allah fi aljanat ma yardaa bh"
  92,21,"wsyuzhzah eanha shadid altqwa, aldhy ybdhl malah abtigha' almazid min alkhyr. walays 'iinfaquh dhak mkafat liman asda 'iilayh merwfa, lknh ybtghy bdhlk wajh rabih al'aelaa wrdah, walasawf yetyh allah fi aljanat ma yardaa bh"
  93,1,"aqsm allah bwqt aldha, walmrad bih alnahar klh, wabiallayl 'iidha sakan bialkhalq washtd zlamh. wyqsm allah bima yasha' min mkhlwqath, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah 'an yuqsim bighayr khalqh, fa'iina alqism bighayr allah shrk. ma trkk -ayha alnby- rbk, wama abghdk b'ibta' alwhy enk"
  93,2,"aqsm allah bwqt aldha, walmrad bih alnahar klh, wabiallayl 'iidha sakan bialkhalq washtd zlamh. wyqsm allah bima yasha' min mkhlwqath, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah 'an yuqsim bighayr khalqh, fa'iina alqism bighayr allah shrk. ma trkk -ayha alnby- rbk, wama abghdk b'ibta' alwhy enk"
  93,3,"'uqsim allah bwqt aldha, walmrad bih alnahar klh, wabiallayl 'iidha sakan bialkhalq washtd zlamh. wyqsm allah bima yasha' min mkhlwqath, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah 'an yuqsim bighayr khalqh, fa'iina alqism bighayr allah shrk. ma trkk -ayha alnby- rbk, wama abghdk b'ibta' alwhy enk"
  93,4,"wlalddar alakhirat khayr lak min dar aldnya, walasawf yuetik rabuk -ayha alnby- min 'anwae al'ineam fi alakhrt, ftrda bdhlk"
  93,5,"wlalddar alakhirat khayr lak min dar aldnya, walasawf yuetik rabuk -ayha alnby- min 'anwae al'ineam fi alakhrt, ftrda bdhlk"
  93,6,"alm yajidk min qbl ytymana, fawak wreak? wawajadak la tadri ma alkitab wala al'iyman, fellamk ma lm takun telm, wwfqk lahsn alaemal? wawajadak fqyrana, fsaq lak rzqk, waghna nafsak balqnaet walsbr?"
  93,7,"alm yajidk min qbl ytymana, fawak wreak? wawajadak la tadri ma alkitab wala al'iyman, fellamk ma lm takun telm, wwfqk lahsn alaemal? wawajadak fqyrana, fsaq lak rzqk, waghna nafsak balqnaet walsbr?"
  93,8,"alm yajidk min qbl ytymana, fawak wreak? wawajadak la tadri ma alkitab wala al'iyman, fellamk ma lm takun telm, wwfqk lahsn alaemal? wawajadak fqyrana, fsaq lak rzqk, waghna nafsak balqnaet walsbr?"
  93,9,"fama alyatim fala tusi meamlth, wa'amaa alsaayil fala tzjrh, bal atemh, waqd hajth, wa'amaa biniemat rabik alty asbghha ealayk fthdth bha"
  93,10,"fama alyatim fala tusi meamlth, wa'amaa alsaayil fala tzjrh, bal atemh, waqd hajth, wa'amaa biniemat rabik alty asbghha ealayk fthdth bha"
  93,11,"fama alyatim fala tusi meamlth, wa'amaa alsaayil fala tzjrh, bal atemh, waqd hajth, wa'amaa biniemat rabik alty asbghha ealayk fthdth bha"
  94,1,"'alam nwse -ayha alnby- lak sadrak lshraye aldyn, waldaewat 'iilaa allh, walatsaf bmkarm alakhlaq, whttna eank bdhlk himlk aldhy athql zhrk, wjelnak -bma 'aneamna ealayk min almkarm- fi mnzlt rafieat ealy?"
  94,2,"alm nwse -ayha alnby- lak sadrak lshraye aldyn, waldaewat 'iilaa allh, walatsaf bmkarm alakhlaq, whttna eank bdhlk himlk aldhy athql zhrk, wjelnak -bma 'aneamna ealayk min almkarm- fi mnzlt rafieat ealy?"
  94,3,"alm nwse -ayha alnby- lak sadrak lshraye aldyn, waldaewat 'iilaa allh, walatsaf bmkarm alakhlaq, whttna eank bdhlk himlk aldhy athql zhrk, wjelnak -bma 'aneamna ealayk min almkarm- fi mnzlt rafieat ealy?"
  94,4,"alm nwse -ayha alnby- lak sadrak lshraye aldyn, waldaewat 'iilaa allh, walatsaf bmkarm alakhlaq, whttna eank bdhlk himlk aldhy athql zhrk, wjelnak -bma 'aneamna ealayk min almkarm- fi mnzlt rafieat ealy?"
  94,5,"fla ythnk 'adhana aedayk ean nashr alrsalt; fa'iina mae aldyq frjana, 'iina mae aldyq frjana"
  94,6,"fla ythnk 'adhana aedayk ean nashr alrsalt; fa'iina mae aldyq frjana, 'iina mae aldyq frjana"
  94,7,"f'idha faraght min 'umur aldunya washghalha fajidd fi alebadt, wa'iilaa rabik wahdah farghab fima endh"
  94,8,"f'idha faraght min 'umur aldunya washghalha fajidd fi alebadt, wa'iilaa rabik wahdah farghab fima endh"